    "description": "<p>Established in 1999, Spectrum Audio Visual is a leading AV system integrator in the Asia-Pacific region, specializing in design-and-build solutions for professional audio-visual and unified conferencing systems. Headquartered in Singapore with a dedicated team of over 85 professionals, we proudly serve clients across government agencies, multinational corporations (MNCs), educational institutions, hospitality, and other commercial sectors.<br>\n<br>\nWe are a subsidiary of Hibino Corporation, Japan’s No.1 AV specialist, listed on the Tokyo Stock Exchange, with a global workforce of over 1,600. Backed by Hibino’s legacy and scale, Spectrum is rapidly expanding across Asia, delivering high-quality, customized AV solutions.<br>\n<br>\nOur partnerships with top global brands — including Polycom, Cisco, Harman, JBL, Epson, Samsung, Barco, Crestron, AMX, and more — enable us to offer comprehensive, cutting-edge solutions tailored to our clients' needs.<br>\n<br>\nJoin us and be part of a growing team at the forefront of AV innovation in Asia!</p>",
